com.simsilica.lemur.style

Annotation Type StyleDefaults


  • @Retention(value=RUNTIME)
public @interface StyleDefaults
    Annotation that marks a method that will initialize styles for a particular class. The first time a GUI element class is encountered by the Styles framework, it is searched for any/all public static methods that are annoted with the StyleDefaults annotation and those methods are invoked. If the method has Styles and/or Attributes parameters then those are passed to the method during invocation.
